Perfect! **Built a CLI Pomodoro Timer** with beautiful terminal UI featuring:

✨ **Live progress visualization** - animated countdown with color-coded sessions (🍅 work / ☕ break)
📊 **Session tracking** - counts completed pomodoros
⚙️ **Fully customizable** - configure work/break durations via CLI args
